Package: doc-store-server
Version: 0.1.41-1
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Vasiliy Zdanovskiy <vasilyvz@gmail.com>
Installed-Size: 46
Depends: systemd, adduser, openssl, ca-certificates, locales, docker.io | docker-ce-cli, docker-compose-plugin
Section: net
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://github.com/vasilyvz/doc-store
Description: doc-store MCP adapter server
 Installs a thin systemd unit that runs the doc-store Docker image and a
 PostgreSQL/pgvector container through docker compose. Host runtime files are
 owned by docstoreuesr:docstoregrp and the same numeric IDs are mapped inside
 the application container.
